Kerala's biggest Open and Free Cyber security meet-up

DEF CON Group Trivandrum organized a Hacker Village which is an open and free cyber security conference, on 11th of may at Bhub, Mar Ivanios campus Nalanchira.
K Sanjay Kumar IPS, Trivandrum City Police Commissioner inaugurated the event along with a talk regarding Cyber security and online crimes affecting children.
Dane Warren, CiSO of Nissan motor corporation, Lince Lawrence, Cyber Security Leader of EY and Rahul Sasi CTO and founder of CloudSek delivered keynote sessions in the hacker village.
The Cyber security leaders talked about the need of Cyber security professionals in the industry, especifically Trivandrum
There were more than 12 speakers and sessions including Connected car hacking, drone hacking etc.
